---
<section class="py-20 md:py-28">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold leading-tight">
      안녕하세요,
      <br />
      <span class="text-(--color-accent) dark:text-(--color-dark-accent)">개발자</span>입니다.
    </h1>
    <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-(--color-text-secondary) dark:text-(--color-dark-text-secondary) max-w-xl">
      기술과 경험을 공유하는 블로그입니다.
    </p>
    <div class="mt-6 flex items-center gap-4">
      <a
        href="/blog"
        class="px-5 py-2.5 rounded-xl bg-(--color-accent) dark:bg-(--color-dark-accent) text-white text-sm font-medium hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity"
      >
        블로그 보기
      </a>
      <a
        href="/about"
        class="px-5 py-2.5 rounded-xl border border-(--color-border) dark:border-(--color-dark-border) text-sm font-medium hover:border-(--color-accent) dark:hover:border-(--color-dark-accent) transition-colors"
      >
        About
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
